HEADWORD: Passional
<hw>Pas"sion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to passion or the passions; exciting, influenced by, or ministering to,
the passions.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A
passionary.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

